            "failure_message": "Requires active grief/sadness (but not at peak) with a clear 'letting go' signal (release) plus at least a trace of calm/relief. Blocks activation if hopeless collapse (despair), high threat states (panic/terror/fear/anxiety/stress), high anger surge (rage/wrath), or shutdown defenses (dissociation/numbness) are dominating. Also requires a settling transition: grief/sadness easing, release/calm rising, or despair/anxiety/stress dropping (optionally with a small lift in hope)."
